HEADWORD: Affectedly
<hw>Af*fect"ed*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In an affected
manner; hypocritically; with more show than reality.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Lovingly; with tender care.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Affectedness</ent>⟦br⟧
